<p itemprop="description">An associate data architect works under guidance to support data architecture activities. They help design and implement data solutions while developing their expertise in data architecture principles and practices.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support the development of data architecture artefacts and documentation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Assist in data modelling activities and data flow design</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Help evaluate data architecture solutions under supervision</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Contribute to data governance and standards implementation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support stakeholder engagement on data architecture matters</li>
    </ul>
</section>

